<s-1 id="RM0000011DA004X_01_0006" proc-id="RM0250U___00000FJ00000">
<ptxt>INSPECT CAMBER, CASTER AND STEERING AXIS INCLINATION</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<s2>
<ptxt>Put the front wheel on the center of the alignment tester.</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="C132440E01" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>Remove the center ornament.</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>Set the camber-caster-king pin gauge and attachment at the center of the axle hub or drive shaft.</ptxt>
</s2>
